author: stsp
msg: On the multi-layer-moves branch, rename a local variable for clarity.
(delete_node): child_subtree_relpath is the relative path portion of
the path the child has been moved-to, rather than the child's pre-move
local relpath. So rename it to child_moved_to_subtree_relpath.

author: kwall
msg: QPID-3825: TransactionTimeoutTest.testProducerOpenCommit and others fails sporadically on slower boxes
The test needs to sync() after sending the last test message in order that the test and broker start
measuring the idle transaction from the same point in time.
